<%= render partial: "partials/navigation" %>
<div class="row fullWidth fullHeight">
  <div class="large-12 columns fullWidth fullHeight">
    <div class="banner fullHeight">
      <div class="cta">
        <div class="display-logo">Prompt Pass<span class="blinking-cursor">|</span></div>
        <div class="tagline">Send secrets with secure two factor messaging</div>
      </div>
      <div class="large-5 medium-7 small-11 demo-form-wrapper">
        <%= simple_form_for sample, as: :sample, url: samples_path, method: :post, html: { class: "pt1" } do |f| %>
          <div class="row p1">
            <div class="medium-12 columns">
              <p class="white-text text-center">Prompt Pass wants to send you a secure message</p>
            </div>
            <%= f.simple_fields_for :recipient do |rf| %>
              <div class="medium-6 columns">
                <label class="white-text">Your Email</label>
                <%= rf.input :email, type: 'email', placeholder: "example@example.com", label: false %>
              </div>
              <div class="medium-6 columns">
                <label class="white-text">Your Phone Number</label>
                <%= rf.input :phone_number, type: 'tel', placeholder: "555-555-5555", label: false %>
              </div>
            <% end %>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="large-12 columns">
                <%= f.button :button, "Send me the message now!", class: "submit" %>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="panel-bg fullWidth">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-12 columns pt1">
      <h3>How it works</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row pt1 howto-section" style="position:relative;">
    <div class="medium-4 columns">
      <p class="howto-step">Write the secret information that you want to send to someone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-4 columns">
      <div class="scene-container">
        <div style="width: 100%; height: 197px; z-index: 900; border: 1px solid #50B1BF; border-radius: 3px;" data-500="top:3%" data-1000="top:100%;" class="howto-icon">
          <div class="p1">Whoa, checkout this cool message that I can send to you through PromptPass! And it's totally secure!</div>
          <button class="fullWidth p1" data-500="opacity:1; display:block" data-800="opacity:0; display:none">Send your message!</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-4 columns">
      <p>You can send whatever you want. Have a password you need to share with a client? Your Grandma's secret recipes? Doesn't matter what it is, all you have to know is that it will be secure.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="panel-bg fullWidth yellow-bg">
  <div class="row pt1 howto-section" style="position:relative;">
    <div class="medium-4 columns">
      <p class="howto-step white-text">Pick an email & phone number to send the link and message to.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-4 columns"></div>
    <div class="medium-4 columns">
      <p class="white-text">As soon as you send your message we will fire off an email to the receiver with a link to your message. We will also send a SMS authentication code to their phone which they'll need to access the secret message.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="panel-bg fullWidth red-bg">
  <div class="row pt1 howto-section" style="position:relative;">
    <div class="medium-4 columns">
      <p class="howto-step white-text">Wait for your recipient to view your secret message.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-4 columns"></div>
    <div class="medium-4 columns">
      <p class="white-text">The person receiving the message can only view the link one time. Once they have view the link the information is destroyed to ensure your secret stays secret.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
